=== sw-cor24-rpg-ii Minimal RPG-II Demo (Indicator-Gated Variant) ===
Program:
H  control header
F  input file INFIL
I  field 01: A0110  (10-char input slice)
I  field 02: A0810  (3-char input tail slice)
C  MOVE01 -> calc work field
O  DETAIL01 output (10 chars) gated by indicator 01
O  DETAIL02 output (3 chars)

Current boundary:
- Real today: one parsed indicator-style gate can now enable or suppress the
  selected O-spec output definition.
- In this variant, MOVE01 clears indicator 01, so the selected gated output
  is suppressed and no detail lines are emitted.

Current runtime-produced output:
(no output)

